examples.en: Today has been a very strenuous day.
Avoid all strenuous exercise until the sprain heals.
On this play he expended many strenuous months.
His strenuous pulling strained his back.
After the operation, you should avoid strenuous exercise.
I don't have the gusto to go on a strenuous hike right now.
Being on a strenuous bender, he had forgotten to sign a cheque.
The proposal has faced strenuous opposition.
